commit message: * Removed unused qbVersion and qbVersionValues from arrays
* Added check for Alternative speed toggle at startup. Now it's disabled by default and it's only enable after checking the status from the API command. This fixes #52
* Added initial implentation for a custom logger
* Added basic report booleans for checking report generation
* Added logging in MainActivity in order to generate a support report
* Added log messages in exception catches for MainActivity

* Added log for settings in Notifier
* Added logs messages for exception and httpcode
* Added end of notification for Notifier
* Added getters and setters for notifierServiceReport and mainActivityReport
* Changed target SDK version to 23
* Changed logs to report while refreshing and in the notification service

* Added report checking in NotificationService
* Added translation for 'Your report is ready' string
* Added handling of intent for sending the report email

* Added report generation in Help menu
* Removed some unused resources
* Added last and current state in report generation
* Removed bracket  characters in log messages

Release 4.2.5

* Added report generation option in Help menu - it fixes #54
* Fixed wrong status for Alternative Speed Limits on startup
